horid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 163, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 14:52", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872654603,45974302,7886]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1241533]嘻哈小树苗[/uid] (2026-06-23 14:50):[/b]<br/><br/>存储麻了啊狼大[/quote]<br/>NM兆易创新3个10CM  存储都不能跌一点了？<br/>他今天不都没跌停。", "lou": 3402, "content_length": 60, "reply_to": 872654603, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782197576}, {"pid": 872655058, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 169, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 14:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "今天收盘大概率就是 纯技术派教科书级别的二买确认<br/>这是造出来的 懂吗？", "lou": 3403, "content_length": 64, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782197654}, {"pid": 872655850, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 176, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 15:00", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "Day 2<br/>机构操盘不如GJD是这样了。", "lou": 3404, "content_length": 29, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782198044}, {"pid": 872657695, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 137, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 15:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "反正今天有色小金属这种大跌 没有什么值得奇怪的<br/>我问你们 从MLCC开始 然后钨 然后钼代替钨 然后六氟化钨 氧化镝 氧化钇到后面碲化锑，钒酸钇 这些你认识吗？我反正不认识<br/>全TM是市场小作文对轰。股价吃到就算了，不会真当这些能反映在业绩里吧？<br/>前面也和你们说了 叫你们去看那几十家澄清的<br/><br/>真正对日替代逻辑的半导体材料票不是还有没加速的么 也没跌破5日线的 不是好好的活在那里？<br/><br/>追高了就说追高了。敢追 就不要嚎", "lou": 3405, "content_length": 371, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782198883}, {"pid": 872661071, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 40, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 15:41", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872659936,45974302,7899]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67145714]Plezl[/uid] (2026-06-23 15:32):[/b]<br/><br/>电池etf跌幅是仅次于有色的，哪怕没有锂矿成分的也是，我不理解[s:ac:喘][/quote]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202606/23/jmQ62-dxs5K7ToS86-1s.jpg[/img]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202606/23/jmQ62-jlenK6ToS87-1o.jpg[/img]<br/>你这不扯么", "lou": 3406, "content_length": 87, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202606/23/jmQ62-dxs5K7ToS86-1s.jpg", "size": 7, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202606/23", "name": "jmQ62-dxs5K7ToS86-1s.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "24"}, {"attachurl": "mon_202606/23/jmQ62-jlenK6ToS87-1o.jpg", "size": 7, "type": "img", "subid": 1, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202606/23", "name": "jmQ62-jlenK6ToS87-1o.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "24"}], "reply_to": 872659936, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782200463}, {"pid": 872661719, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 182, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 15:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我发现你们盘中盘外都是喜欢情绪主导操作和思想<br/>完全不看事实<br/>我觉得真到了挂顶上 你们一定是挂得最高的那些。甚至比那些不会炒股的挂的还多<br/><br/>两融已经3WE了 带杠杆跑步进场的资金就是你们吧", "lou": 3407, "content_length": 171, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782200774}, {"pid": 872697929, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 140, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 21:51", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872697297,45974302,7918]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64465297]13k小黑子[/uid] (2026-06-23 21:44):[/b]<br/><br/>炸了 就一个加息和韩国去杠杆？[/quote]<br/><br/>对 所以等美股开盘跟亚盘低开，然后修复就行了<br/>因为我们是T+1 量化接受到小作文会先砸 机构也没办法<br/>这是底层逻辑", "lou": 3408, "content_length": 106, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 872697297, "postdatetimestamp": 1782222719}, {"pid": 872698957, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 129, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 22:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872698452,45974302,7918]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65490615]子午卯酉甲乙丙丁[/uid] (2026-06-23 21:58):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大。现在主线还是光 存 导(设备 材料) 算力么？有没有板块掉队的了，比如设备是不是预期已经到头了[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/><br/>设备ETF今年涨幅是通信ETF的翻倍<br/>这句话我有没有改过", "lou": 3409, "content_length": 53, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 872698452, "postdatetimestamp": 1782223475}, {"pid": 872699912, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 84, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 22:15", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872699396,45974302,7919]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65490615]子午卯酉甲乙丙丁[/uid] (2026-06-23 22:09):[/b]<br/><br/>但是狼大，请教一下。中大哥是总龙头的话，不仅仅是代表光了对吧。其实是整个大科技做多的总龙头[/quote]<br/><br/>对 他不能出负反馈", "lou": 3410, "content_length": 21, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 872699396, "postdatetimestamp": 1782224119}, {"pid": 872734155, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 257, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 09:56", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "胆子那么小你们就别炒股了  出去卖茶叶蛋吧", "lou": 3411, "content_length": 38, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782266193}, {"pid": 872737575, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 196, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 10:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872737346,45974302,7953]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64973700]SpamSender[/uid] (2026-06-24 10:18):[/b]<br/><br/>这种外面4000+待涨的行情是对的[/quote]<br/>对 市场只能涨我的就对了 就要这种心态 股市本来就是1赚2平7亏<br/>一将功成万骨枯  他们只配给我做垫脚尸", "lou": 3412, "content_length": 94, "reply_to": 872737346, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782267586}, {"pid": 872737935, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 134, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 10:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我新能源+半导体<br/>我怕什么<br/>我怕挣钱？<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>明天我减一点半导体的利润出来  继续加我的新能源。", "lou": 3413, "content_length": 79, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782267739}, {"pid": 872738391, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 90, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 10:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872737977,45974302,7954]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65490615]子午卯酉甲乙丙丁[/uid] (2026-06-24 10:22):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，现在大科技板块权重其实也不低了，机构也没有必要拉那些老权重控指数了吧？直接把中大哥拉起来也够用了[/quote]<br/>我已经说过了  这波最后拉升是为了出货。这些大票拉不高的  因为要出货  他们能不跌就行<br/>或者说我要在他出完货开始跌之前赚到更多的钱 然后跑路", "lou": 3414, "content_length": 131, "reply_to": 872737977, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782267919}, {"pid": 872738920, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 955, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 10:29", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我TM已经说了啊  我今天尾盘或者明天减仓半导体。听懂的打111<br/><br/>噢 不能刷屏 你们点赞就行了 <br/><br/>别等下傻了吧唧说  科技为什么还没涨就要减啊 <br/><br/>MD连K线都不会看的。", "lou": 3415, "content_length": 138, "14": {"13": 1}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782268140}, {"pid": 872746583, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 303, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 11:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "半导体连涨十几天  甚至下跌通道都没跌 你们在嚎<br/>那黄线那些微盘股怎么办？下跌通道吃满 好不容易昨天反弹一天 今天直接闷杀。这些人比你们还淡定 有一股微死的宁静。<br/>好好看盘就行了。你们拿的票和时间都已经比市场上90%的票都好了 知足吧<br/>别人还在看自己的票会不会新低<br/>我们已经在讨论止盈位了<br/><br/>你们是不是觉得股市挣钱很简单？<br/>你们也能和我一样判断出资金的切换方向？", "lou": 3416, "content_length": 331, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782271219}, {"pid": 872747570, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 109, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 11:26", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872747199,45974302,7972]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60925933]ywlight2468[/uid] (2026-06-24 11:24):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，锂矿今天也这么厉害的，电池是不是优先&amp;#128064;矿啊[/quote]<br/>我说了 新能源你们爱做什么就做什么 <br/>我只做锂电和电网<br/>我有我自己的操作逻辑", "lou": 3417, "content_length": 73, "reply_to": 872747199, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782271611}, {"pid": 872756402, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 93, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 12:31", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872755308,45974302,7982]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66879286]爱灯痴[/uid] (2026-06-24 12:22):[/b]<br/><br/>还有茂莱光学[/quote]<br/>总算还有一两个正常人<br/>菜归菜 能记事", "lou": 3418, "content_length": 37, "reply_to": 872755308, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782275475}, {"pid": 872758859, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 108, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-24 12:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872758603,45974302,7985]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=41880243]峰城大附属学生保护协会[/uid] (2026-06-24 12:51):[/b]<br/><br/>6.15-6.17那两天我就是这么想的然后出了一半铁盒，没想到还能涨[s:ac:晕]<br/>今天茂莱没破前高，算是正确信号了吧[s:ac:呆][/quote]<br/>你那明明是被菜鸡图吓出去的  扯什么自己想的", "lou": 3419, "content_length": 45, "reply_to": 872758603, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782276861}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 172949, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782914706, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "rlshjsi", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782914759, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 6, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,66985104,19043499,39108806,41714633,7046671,65647302,40696141,3481707,654677,39235785,66063392,39314790,67071606,66251279,42126891,61602239,4785041,42995612,67024871,62241578,64199867,11586486,5641907,66685489,66633842,65208818,42941765,,42964685,42181525,14317962,67086252,34699482,6